com.vanna.facultyprofiling.datastore

Annotation Type ExcelRepository


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ExcelRepository
    The ExcelRepository annotation is used for the Repository linking to a specific model. The annotation has to be used at the class level of the Repository. mapsTo points to the composite class that has been used in the list of the form's model. aggregateClass points to the class that contains a List of the composite class mentioned in the mapsTo.

    1.0
